{"id": "1407662842210942976", "channel_id": "1407662842210942976", "type": 0, "author_id": "145604823151149057", "author_name": "miku__", "author_bot": false, "content": "I very recently downloaded the game clearly. I have not used any of the free ssr items they so generously give out pretty quickly. So my main questions are basically what characters I should focus building right now,  and is there like anything to do that is not story or just a story grind, and what to do with the free characters.", "timestamp": "2025-08-20T09:49:34.694000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1407662842668257310", "filename": "Screenshot_20250820-123743.Morimens.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2358810, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1407662842210942976/1407662842668257310/Screenshot_20250820-123743.Morimens.png?ex=69ccea2e&is=69cb98ae&hm=31c05e09d68e8be75505cf26c72d466e96ec579fd5a99554bbacc5db7265a738&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407662842210942976", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "What to focus on", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747333490184292"]}
{"id": "1407669562819739738", "channel_id": "1407662842210942976", "type": 0, "author_id": "885715464775413831", "author_name": "limewareplatter", "author_bot": false, "content": "You'll unlock more content as you level. There's event stages, D-tide (endgame where you have 5 stages that you can't re-use wheels or characters on so you really need a wide roster + wheels) Daily Dive, Weekly Boss material farm stages, Lightless Realm Stages which are more of a one time clear thing, Character Story unlock stages.\n\nIt looks like you're spreading your standard pulls about? That's not generally great practice. This game is pretty dupe reliant so you want to focus on a banner. Pull on the Realm Study Blue/Aeqour till you get E3 Caecus, and maybe Goliath E2. Then off to wheel jail for Blade of the Titan.\n\nFor limited pulls, I'd focus on grabbing a Copy of Thais and her wheel right now. When the new banner comes grab a copy of Horla and Hameln. Corposant is also a great blue character but probably a little lower priority than the others mentioned. \n\nSince doll isn't there I assume that's not your entire roster. It'd be best to show your entire roster for picking teams.\n \nStory content is pretty dang easy till chapter 5. I think I cleared the first few chapters with the default team so you don't need to worry too much for a while. Every Character you are currently showing has some purpose in Dtide. Most are missing some important enlightens to fill out their kit but that'll come with time.\n\nYou could do Goliath, Nautila, Karen/Ramona/Celeste, Caecus for an early team. Goliath's exalt + usurp will clear early mobs really quickly. If you look in the guides here there's a speedrun strat by Aurora you can also use. Once you grab Thais you can upgrade to this Goliath speedrun team based on the Aurora team that can supposedly clear all of act1: https://www.reddit.com/r/Morimens/comments/1mektsi/since_thais_banner_is_up_now_here_is_a_beginner/#lightbox", "timestamp": "2025-08-20T10:16:17.012000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "article", "title": "From the Morimens community on Reddit: Since thais banner is up now...", "url": "https://www.reddit.com/r/Morimens/comments/1mektsi/since_thais_banner_is_up_now_here_is_a_beginner/", "description": "Explore this post and more from the Morimens community"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407662842210942976", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "What to focus on", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747333490184292"]}
